title: [Whistler's Pass, Rocky Ledge]
description: A dead branch falls from a tree far below, the cracking sound filling the gap between the mountains with a sharp, staccato echo.  A night hawk patrols the sky beneath the ledge, barely visible as it turns sleepy ovals amidst the moonlit peaks.
